<!--
Provides the ability to introduce superadmins

Features:
- introduces the superadmin role:
  initially only the first admin created has the superadmin abilities (so he/she needs to make others superadmin)
- only superadmins have access to site administration (this is not air tight but blocks access to all pg/admin/* pages)
- in the plugin setting you can control if normal admins can make other normal admin or can delete users (default this is disabled for normal admins)

Version history:

0.1:
	- initial release
	
-->
